"Language: it\n"

msgctxt "0||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san, do you go to shrines?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1||||4"
msgid "Shrines... Yeah, I visit them sometimes."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2||||4"
msgid "Me too. The wind feels so good over there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3||||4"
msgid "Since you asked, do you ever go to them?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4||||4"
msgid "I just went yesterday. Hoping it'll bless me with good luck."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5||||4"
msgid "You're so small-minded."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||||4"
msgid "So did something good happen?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7||||4"
msgid "Nothing really, but I did witness something odd."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8||||4"
msgid "Odd?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9||||4"
msgid "I saw Kaneko-san shadowboxing earlier."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11||||4"
msgid "Y-You saw that...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12||||4"
msgid "Kaneko-san... you..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13||||4"
msgid "You must really love boxing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||||4"
msgid "I see."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "15||||4"
msgid "Huh? What did you say?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "16||||4"
msgid "S-Sorry, I was thinking about something else..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||||4"
msgid "Well, it's not something to be embarassed about."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "18||||4"
msgid "He's right. All men do that now and then."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19||||4"
msgid "You said it was odd..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "20||||4"
msgid "I used to shadowbox against my room lamp as a kid."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "21||||4"
msgid "Don't compare me to you as a kid! Geez."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "22||||4"
msgid "Kaneko-san used to be an actual boxer."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "23||||4"
msgid "Wh-Whaaaaaat!? Seriously!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||||4"
msgid "First I'm hearing of it..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||||4"
msgid "It was a long time ago."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "26||||4"
msgid "Wait, why does only Mama know?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "27||||4"
msgid "I know everything."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||||4"
msgid "Then tell me my bust, waist, and hip measurements."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "29||||4"
msgid "All about 129.3 cm probably."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||||4"
msgid "I don't think so. Forget it..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "31||||4"
msgid "A boxer, huh? Did you have to watch your weight and stuff?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "32||||4"
msgid "Of course. There were times I even had to limit my water intake."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "33||||4"
msgid "Wooow, what a stoic life."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "34||||4"
msgid "But then you go all out on delicious meals after a match, no?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||||4"
msgid "Yeah, is that true, Kaneko-san?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||||4"
msgid "After a match, the stomach rejects food, so I can't eat right away."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "37||||4"
msgid "Well... that's something..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "38||||4"
msgid "Nowadays, I hear people make diet adjustments with their trainers."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||||4"
msgid "Did you quit because it was too tough?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "40||||4"
msgid "Don't be an idiot. Of course not."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||||4"
msgid "I went through a lot of other shit."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||||4"
msgid "Why don't you give boxing a try too, Mama?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||||4"
msgid "I hear that women are getting into it lately."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||||4"
msgid "Oh, that boxer-cize thing?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||||4"
msgid "I saw on TV that it's effective for shaping your body."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||||4"
msgid "Mama boxer-cizing..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||||4"
msgid "Mama might look good toned."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||||4"
msgid "You think so?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "49||||4"
msgid "Hm? What's going on?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||||4"
msgid "S-Sorry, I dozed off for a bit."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "51||||4"
msgid "But I'd have mixed feelings if Mama was stronger than me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||||4"
msgid "As a man, you know...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "53||||4"
msgid "I'll fight people off who mess with you, Akiyoshi-kun!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "54||||4"
msgid "I-I'll look like a loser! I'll pick up boxing too!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||||4"
msgid "You're seriously small-minded..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||||4"
msgid "I guess I'll have Kaneko-san teach me then."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||||4"
msgid "Hell no. I'm already a retired man."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||||4"
msgid "Just let me forget about boxing..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "59||||4"
msgid "But Kaneko-san, don't you think you seem kinda flabby?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||||4"
msgid "Do ya think he let himself go?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||||4"
msgid "Do I seem out of shape...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||||4"
msgid "In that case..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||||4"
msgid "Why don't you exercise with me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||||4"
msgid "With Kiryu-san?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||||4"
msgid "Yeah, I always try to keep active."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||||4"
msgid "Sounds like a good idea to avoid putting on more weight!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "67||||4"
msgid "Whoa whoa, knock it off."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||||4"
msgid "Shadowboxing isn't enough to slim you down, Kaneko-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "69||||4"
msgid "Shut up! Enough about that!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "70||||4"
msgid "Hahah!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "71||||4"
msgid "No, it's fine..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||||4"
msgid "You can't keep boozing without exercising. It's unhealthy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "73||||4"
msgid "You're not gonna attract the ladies like that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||||4"
msgid "Shut up. Leave me alone..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "75||||4"
msgid "(That was a rather dull ending...)"
msgstr ""

